      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:2:1:151:1",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) سِبَابُ الْمُؤْمِنِ كَالْمُشْرِفِ عَلَى الْهَلَكَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘The insulter of the <span class=\"iTxt\">Momin</span> is like one on the verge of the destruction’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from al-Nawfali from al-Sakuni from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “The Messenger of Allah has said, ‘Reviling a believer is like one’s positioning one’s self at the verge of destruction. ’” "
        ]
      }
